title: Microsoft 365: Group-based licensing
agents: microsoft_365
catalog: cloud/Microsoft
license: GPLv2
distribution: Christopher Pommer
description:
 This check monitors the Microsoft group-based licensing errors
 from a Microsoft 365 tenant.

 The service is in state {OK} if there are no group-based licensing errors
 and in state {CRIT} if there is one or more group-based licensing errors.

 You have to configure the special agent {Microsoft 365}.

discovery:
 One service is created for group-based licensing errors.